videos.headline: Missouri strikes back with Star Wars troll after win vs. Florida
videos.description: After Florida coach Dan Mullen dressed up as Darth Vader following the Gators' win in 2020, Missouri coach Eliah Drinkwitz pulls out a lightsaber after the Tigers' win on Saturday.

videos.headline: Two-point conversion in OT lifts Mizzou to victory
videos.description: In a back-and-forth defensive battle, the Tigers become bowl eligible by converting a two-point conversion to beat Florida, 24-23.
